# ⚡ Bit Manipulation Cheatsheet

        **🧠 Memory Aid:** AND clears, OR sets, XOR toggles.  n & (n-1) clears rightmost set bit — used for popcount and power-of-2 checks. 


## 🔧 Bitwise Operators
       `// AND, OR, XOR, NOT, SHL, SHR
// 1010 & 1100 = 1000
// 1010 | 1100 = 1110
// 1010 ^ 1100 = 0110
// ~1010 = ...0101
// 1  > 2 = 4`
